            "text": "A Musical Story",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " follows a young man named Gabriel who is lying unconscious in a hospital bed. Help Gabriel come to terms with his situation through the connections to his musical memory in this beautifully crafted rhythm game set against a 70s backdrop where every correctly played melody reveals more of Gabriel’s past, leading him closer to the truth.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
