      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "When I played the demo for this game last year, it felt like the timing to hit the notes was a little strict. In that time, the developers have eased up on this but at times, it feels like the timing is now too lenient. There have been times when I’ve accidentally hit a button in haste, only for the game to register that I hit a note two notes down in the timeline.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
